T02TD3698E:329a-1: brahma pu tr'i sva ra sa tyee sto tre na siddham w'a ka pra bha n'a ma /
T02TD3698E:329a-3: tshangs pa'i bu mo dbyangs can ma la bstod pas grub pa dag gi 'od zer zhes bya ba /
T02TD3698E:329a-5: spyan ras gzigs dbang zhal gyi mche ba'i rtse las mngon sprul zhing //
T02TD3698E:329a-6: thugs rje'i rnam 'phrul mtha' yas pha rol rjes su gzung ba'i phyir //
T02TD3698E:329a-7: tshangs pa'i bu mo mdzes ma khyod sku gsal ba'i rnam 'gyur can //
T02TD3698E:329a-8: bishnu'i gzugs can tambu ra la dga' bskyed tshul 'dzin ma //
T02TD3698E:329b-0: @329b rjes su chags bcas rol pa'i lo ni bcu drug lon pa'i nyams //
T02TD3698E:329b-1: chu gter 'gram ngogs lbu ba'i phreng bas rtse bar dga' ba can //
T02TD3698E:329b-2: dri za'i bu mo mngon bstod nyid kyi rnam thar phul byung rnams //
T02TD3698E:329b-3: gang gis yid la dran byed de la ngag gi dbang phyug stsol //
T02TD3698E:329b-4: kho bos khyod dran ba spu shas cher g-yo ba'i lag pa gnyis //
T02TD3698E:329b-5: thal sbyar me tog gzhon nu kha 'bus lta bu spyi bo'i steng //
T02TD3698E:329b-6: rab bzhag snying nas rab tu gus pa lhur byed khyod kyi yon tan ni //
T02TD3698E:329b-7: mtha' dag rtogs min cung zang rnyed 'di sdeb legs phreng bas mchod //
T02TD3698E:329b-8: khyod sku 'o ma'i mtsho 'dra kunda ku mud zla zer mtshungs //
T02TD3698E:329b-9: rab dkar 'od kyi phreng bas kun nas bskor ba'i gzi brjid kyis //
T02TD3698E:329b-10: lha dbang yid 'phrog dga' ba'i nga ros khyod la rtag tu bstod byed na //
T02TD3698E:329b-11: blo gros don gsal don gnyer lha la gus pa smos ci dgos //
T02TD3698E:329b-12: chu skyes dkar po dri med steng gnas ge sar g-yo ba'i rtser //
T02TD3698E:329b-13: ri bong 'dzin pa'i gdan steng tsog pu'i tshul bzhugs bgying bag can //
T02TD3698E:329b-14: zhal gcig phyag gnyis dri za'i pi wang bsgrengs pa'i sgra dbyangs dang //
T02TD3698E:329b-15: rjes mthun gsung gis sa gsum skye dgu'i bsam pa tshim mdzad ma //
T02TD3698E:329b-16: 'jam mnyen 'khril zhing ring ba bung ba lta bur gnag pa'i skra //
T02TD3698E:329b-17: g-yas g-yon rgyab tu 'phyang zhing cung zad li ba'i thor cog la //
T02TD3698E:329b-18: me tog dkar po'i phreng bas thod bcings spyi gtsug zla bas spud //
T02TD3698E:329b-19: gser gyi rna cha 'phyang zhing mkhur tshos mdzes pa 'dzum pa'i zhal //
T02TD3698E:329b-20: ka tsa linda'i smad g-yogs tshom bu'i spras pas sgeg pa'i nyams //
T02TD3698E:329b-21: punda r'i ka'i phreng ba chun 'phyang mgul rgyan do shal can //
T02TD3698E:329b-22: phyag zhabs rin chen phreng ba sil sil sgra ldan brgyus pa yis //
T02TD3698E:329b-23: khyed sku lha dang rig 'dzin bu mo'i tshogs kun ngo mtshar gyur //
T02TD3698E:329b-24: lha mo gzhon sgeg lang tshor ldan pa skye dgu'i yid 'phrog ma //
T02TD3698E:329b-25: yid 'ong 'dzum pa'i bzhin can mig dkyus ring po'i zur gyis ni //
T02TD3698E:329b-26: smin ma g-yo ba'i gar can khyod sku rtag tu dran byed la //
T02TD3698E:329b-27: rab tu dgyes pa'i nyams kyis gzigs shing kho bo rjes su bzung //
T02TD3698E:329b-28: mdzad spyod bags kyis dal zhing gsong por smra ba'i ngang tshul can //
T02TD3698E:330a-1: pa'i dri ldan nu zho nu bar 'dod pa la //
T02TD3698E:330a-2: reg pas dga' ba'i nu zho stob byed khyed la rtag tu bstod pa'i bu //
T02TD3698E:330a-3: snying nas yus che shas cher du ba'i gdung ba tshim mdzad ma //
T02TD3698E:330a-4: de yi yid la bstod pa'i zol tshig ca cor ma nges pa yi sgra //
T02TD3698E:330a-5: smra ba'i ga zhas 'dir spel nyid kyi thugs la bas gyur mod //
T02TD3698E:330a-6: 'on kyang kho bo'i blo ni 'dir zad bu yi nyes pa rnams //
T02TD3698E:330a-7: ma yis bzod mdzad brtse bas slar yang bu ni rab tu skyongs //
T02TD3698E:330a-8: snying gi chu skyes 'dab brgyad dkar po ze'u 'bru'i phreng ba can //
T02TD3698E:330a-9: dmar ser mdzes pa'i mtshams nas 'od kyi dra ba rab tu dgye //
T02TD3698E:330a-10: ge sar 'jam pa'i rtse mor bsil zer can ni rab gnas pa'i //
T02TD3698E:330a-11: dbus su chu shel mdog 'dzin hr'im gi phreng bas sgrib gnyis 'joms //
T02TD3698E:330a-12: 'dab ma re rer gnyis gnyis bzhugs pa'i aa a'a la sogs dbyangs yig rnams //
T02TD3698E:330a-13: g-yas su bskor ba'i rim pas mar me'i phreng ba 'bar ba ltar //
T02TD3698E:330a-14: kun nas 'od zer 'phro ba'i rgyan ldan rtse mo'i rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD3698E:330a-15: yid kyi dri ma mun nag rnam bsal blo gros mchog stsol mdzod //
T02TD3698E:330a-16: srog gi 'od zer skra yi khyod tsam phra ba'i cha shas kyis //
T02TD3698E:330a-17: rtsol ba'i sgo nas myur bar lha mo'i thugs la reg gyur pas //
T02TD3698E:330a-18: 'khor lo gnyis pa bskor bas rnam pa bdun pa'i mchod sprin can //
T02TD3698E:330a-19: 'jug pa'i rlung zhon rang sems ye shes rgyas mdzad de la 'dud //
T02TD3698E:330a-20: de rjes hr'im gi phreng ba mu tig do shal mgal me yi //
T02TD3698E:330a-21: 'khor ba'i tshul du 'khor ba zhal gyis go nas 'thon gyur cing //
T02TD3698E:330a-22: lte ba'i dkyil 'khor nas zhugs slar yang sa bon tsha zer rtser //
T02TD3698E:330a-23: 'bar ba'i mod la dbyangs can ngag ster khyod zhabs spyi bos blang //
T02TD3698E:330a-24: lha mo gtsang spra la dga' brdzun spangs 'byung po'i zas dor zhing //
T02TD3698E:330a-25: tshangs spyod brtul zhugs can gyis nyin re dran byas yum bos na //
T02TD3698E:330a-26: slar yang dag gi dbang phyug ci bzhed gsungs pa'i gad mo yis //
T02TD3698E:330a-27: dkar gsum zas kyi dga' ston tshul gyis dngos grub stsol la 'dud //
T02TD3698E:330a-28: de ltar khyod bstod lhur len gang yin de ni yon tan gyis //
T02TD3698E:330a-29: dbul gyur sna tshogs rigs pa'i gzhung lugs rnams las nges pa'i don //
T02TD3698E:330b-0: myur @330b rtogs sa gsum skye bo'i gzhung sgron gti mug mun pa rnams //
T02TD3698E:330b-1: rab bsal rgyal ba'i dbang po 'od dpag med 'dra thob par shog /'dir ni 'phags dang mkhas pa'i skye bo phul byung chogs rnams ston //
T02TD3698E:330b-2: bdag 'dra khums shing mu cor sgrogs pa dang tshul mi shes mod //
T02TD3698E:330b-3: khyod kyi rjes zhugs lan cig ma yin tshig don goms bya'i phyir //
T02TD3698E:330b-4: sdeb sbyor gtsor byas brag ca'i sgra mtshungs 'di ni bstod par rigs //
T02TD3698E:330b-5: tshig 'di gang gis mthong ngam thos sam rtag tu dran byed dam //
T02TD3698E:330b-6: klog dang kha don byed dang bsam don chub byed pa //
T02TD3698E:330b-7: yi ger bri'am gzhan la rgya cher rab tu ston kyang rung //
T02TD3698E:330b-8: de yi sems dang ngag la dpal ldan lha mo dbyangs can myur 'jug shog / tshangs pa'i bu mo dbyangs can ma la bstod pas grub pa ngag gi 'od zer zhes bya ba //
T02TD3698E:330b-9: lha mo nyid kyis dngos su byin gyis brlabs pa'i bram ze phur bus mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3698E:330b-11: // / sum pa lo ts'a ba dar ma yon tan gyis bsgyur ba'o//
